govelect lowell p weicker jr said 
wednesday connecticuts budget problems may get worse and he is 
weighing all options including tax increases to deal with a 21 
billion shortfall 
ill have to study it said weicker a former threeterm 
us senator 
well get whatever job has to be done done weicker said 
i think its clear to anybody that sacrifice is going to be 
required in some form and i dont want to go ahead and state what 
the sacrifice is going to be until i understand the full dimensions 
of the problems 
