terrorism discovered the existence of gladio during a probe of a 
rightwing terrorist attack and has asked president francesco 
cossiga to testify about the group 
in greece where the anticommunist network was known as 
sheepskin caches with arms ammunition torches and other 
equipment were dug up between 1985 and 1988 when the network was 
dismantled 
