by casual drug users and thats white uppermiddle class 
americans that drive their pontiac firebirds into the ghetto and 
buy these killer drugs solomon said 
you dont see the murders take place out in the suburbs but 
its the casual drug user who supplies the demand for these 
drugs he said if you do away with the demand for drugs then 
the drugs will dry up in this country when it starts to affect 
their livelihoods maybe then theyll stop using these drugs 
but license suspensions wouldnt necessarily affect their 
livelihoods because they would receive limited driving permits 
enabling them to continue commuting to work he said 
