exclusion of the mention of ethnic origin he said 
the issue is a sensitive one in rwanda where bloody power 
struggles have resulted in brutal ethnic retaliation in the late 
1950s hundreds of thousands of the minority tutsi fled the country 
after the hutu seized control and killed thousands of their former 
feudal rulers 
