industry minister lee hsien loong 38 the prime ministers eldest 
son to serve as one of his two deputies 
that came as no surprise goh acknowledged earlier that the 
younger lee was his logical successor as prime minister 
now however goh finds it necessary to insist he will not play 
a transitional role to keep the seat warm for the leaders 
ambitious son 
