<TEXT>
but his debut lp in 1972 cold spring harbor was mastered 
at the wrong speed so he played piano bars under the name bill 
martin and gathered material for his hit debut album for columbia 
piano man in 1973 
his problems however were far from over 
i signed away a lot of things in those early days he said 
