his father left home when joel was 7 he considered suicide and 
checked himself into a mental institution in his early 20s 
fractured his right wrist and left thumb in a 1982 motorcycle 
accident that put his career in jeopardy and was divorced in 1982 
after a nineyear marriage to elizabeth weber his nose still shows 
signs of the 26 amateur fights he had at age 19 
it always amazes me the resilience of human beings its 
unbelievable but im happy to be anywhere he said with a laugh 
im as old as a 49 studebaker ever look at a car from 1949 
the steel is all rusted out the body is all dented and falling 
apart the upholstery is all ripped and the engine doesnt work 
i look in the mirror and say well you aint cary grant but 
you aint in the junkyard either but im happy with my life 
very happy its nothing at all like i pictured it would be 
