eastern airlines and its creditors were at odds 
today over a multimilliondollar cash infusion that would keep the 
troubled airline flying into december 
the creditors argued in us bankruptcy court that eastern 
cannot become viable they want to sell the remaining assets and 
close the final chapter in the tortuous legacy of the 
