<TEXT>
gap inc is a proud parent again 
after downscaling its trendy gap apparel line into kid sizes 
the california retailer has further miniaturized its offerings for 
the newborntotoddler set 
the first babygap appeared just nine months ago in a corner of a 
gap store in san francisco since then the company has spawned 
babygap departments within 50 of its 150 gapkids stores that dot 
the nations shopping landscape 
though still in its infancy industry analysts say babygap has 
become a roaring success story based on the same formula that 
catapulted the company to the status of industry darling durable 
clothing in comfortable generous cuts at affordable prices 
indeed gap went against the tide by selecting quality suppliers 
that do not normally manufacture childrens clothing to create a 
hybrid of better quality and fun fashion which is unique in kids 
merchandising said thomas tashjian an analyst with seidler 
amdek securities inc in los angeles 
for parents who cringe at swathing their little ones in 
synthetic fabrics babygap offerings are strictly 100 percent 
sturdy cotton banished from shelves are those anemic 
genderidentifying pastels only deep bold hues can be found on 
everything from rugbystriped jumpsuits to raime vneck pullovers 
and crisp embroidered blouses in tiny sizes where else can you 
find a singlepocket tshirt in black for a 1yearold a gap 
spokesman asked rhetorically 
the seasonal color palette and natural fibers are what attracted 
laura cooper a mother from brooklyn ny to the babygap shops in 
manhattan shortly after they opened 
what they do well is edit each of the lines so that youre not 
overwhelmed with what to choose from cooper said and individual 
items available in an array of colors make for an easy way to put 
together a complementary wardrobe she said 
because gap turns over its merchandise very frequently cooper 
heads straight for the sale sign though gap spokesman richard 
crisman said the company is not in the business of offering sale 
racks he conceded merchandise is set aside to make way for fresh 
offerings which arrive every six weeks or so 
you will find a new color palette and new designs every six 
weeks it may be the same tshirt but it might be in a new 
color or we may have added a detail he said 
the babygap was the logical outgrowth of gapkids which was 
created in 1985 out of gap president millard mickey drexlers 
search for stylish but longlasting clothing for his own young son 
drexler who rarely speaks to the press voiced his frustrations to 
staff members and realized how tired others also were of pink and 
blue crisman said 
originally the kids clothes were simply scaleddown versions of 
the adult line but once executives realized what a hit they had on 
their hands gap established a team to design just the childrens 
line 
because the kids stores are smaller partially to minimize the 
risk in launching the line and also because the merchandise is 
well smaller sales per square foot outpace that of gap stores 
already among the highest in the industry analysts have estimated 
gap sales at about 360 a square foot babygap at 400 
even in this dismal retail environment the gap is expected to 
fare well during the crucial holiday season mainly because it is a 
lean operation with low fixed costs and price tags that will not 
send recessionweary consumers into cardiac arrest bigsellers in 
the baby department are the denim overalls for 28 embroidered 
blouses for 16 and longsleeve tshirts in bright blue purple 
yellow or red for 10 
donald trott an analyst with dean witter reynolds inc 
estimates that gap will report earnings of 182 a share for the 
fiscal year ending jan 31 1991 up from 138 the previous year 
sales are expected to total 194 billion up from 159 billion 
their growth rate has been running at around 20 percent a 
year and it is expected to continue to run at that pace he 
said gapkids is certainly helping that growth rate in terms 
of total contribution babygap is not significant yet but we think 
it has good potential 
many gapkids stores are located either within or in sight of 
regular gap stores in an effort to piggyback customer traffic 
theres a benefit to both crisman said 
having childrens and adult clothing under the same roof allows 
consumers to do all their shopping at one time but separate 
childrens stores eliminates the problem of kids who dont want 
to be shopping in the same store as their parents crisman said 
the companys latest strategy is to open even bigger stores that 
can expand the product line and incorporate adult kids and baby 
gear all under one roof 
gapkids and babygap are a significant part of gaps future the 
company plans to open more than 40 new gap stores in 1991 it will 
open just as many gapkids with babygap departments 
we dont do anything here in a big way until we are entirely 
sure of it and this is going gangbusters crisman said 
the company which also owns the banana republic chain is 
expanding its gap stores in britain and canada the first 
freestanding gapkids store opened in london earlier this year 
the regular line already has 750 stores and there isnt 
any reason why the kids line cant follow along the parents 
coattails in terms of success analyst tashjian said 
perhaps gaps greatest achievement has been its ability to 
capitalize on the handing down of tradition most middleclass 
babyboomers grew up with some relationship with the gap now their 
children can be clad in similar fare all exclusive to the gap 
</TEXT>
